{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"9984d6ec-adc1-409e-b520-87109d5c91b4","content":"The process PID 12345 doesn't exist on this machine. No worries — here's how to diagnose and configure dumps on your actual host:\n\n---\n\n### 1. Determine the runtime\n\n```bash\n# Check for CoreCLR shared libraries in the process\ncat /proc/<PID>/maps | grep -i coreclr\n```\n\n- **If you see `libcoreclr.so`** → it's **CoreCLR**.\n- **If there's no `libcoreclr.so`** → it's likely **NativeAOT** (a statically-linked, self-contained binary).\n\nYou can also check:\n```bash\n# NativeAOT binaries won't have these\nls -l /proc/<PID>/maps | grep -iE 'libhostfxr|libclrjit'\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. Configure crash dumps\n\n#### For CoreCLR\n\nSet these environment variables before launching the app:\n\n```bash\nexport DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump=1\nexport DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType=4          # 1=Mini, 2=Heap, 3=Triage, 4=Full\nexport DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName=/tmp/dumps/coredump.%p.%t\nmkdir -p /tmp/dumps\n```\n\nType 4 (Full) gives the most complete dump for debugging.\n\n#### For NativeAOT\n\nNativeAOT doesn't use the `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump` settings. Use the **OS-level core dump mechanism** instead:\n\n```bash\n# Set core dump pattern\necho '/tmp/dumps/core.%e.%p.%t' | sudo tee /proc/sys/kernel/core_pattern\n\n# Remove core file size limit\nulimit -c unlimited\n\nmkdir -p /tmp/dumps\n```\n\n#### For either runtime (belt-and-suspenders)\n\nYou can configure **both** — the OS-level `core_pattern` works for any process, and the `DOTNET_DbgMiniDump*` vars are simply ignored by NativeAOT:\n\n```bash\n# OS-level (works for both)\necho '/tmp/dumps/core.%e.%p.%t' | sudo tee /proc/sys/kernel/core_pattern\nulimit -c unlimited\n\n# CoreCLR-specific (harmless if NativeAOT)\nexport DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump=1\nexport DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType=4\nexport DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName=/tmp/dumps/coredump.%p.%t\n\nmkdir -p /tmp/dumps\n```\n\nThis way you're covered regardless of the runtime.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"3191183b-4f2b-43ae-89f9-d6d367194a07","outputTokens":658,"requestId":"D819:1E62:29C9D91:2E2A826:69FBF13D"},"id":"73407318-bbf0-4072-ac64-361d251d9b19","timestamp":"2026-05-07T01:56:27.067Z","parentId":"88627d02-ce95-4e85-8c77-a740e7ce0c98"}
